rved ones. We have applied\nthe model to the first 176 planets confirmed by the TESS, finding that, from an\nastrobiological perspective TOI-700 d and TOI-2257 b are the most interesting\nones as being located in the habitable zone (HZ), although their magnetic\nmoments are only about 0.01 of the Earth's magnetic moment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Mar 2022 12:32:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-25"}
